# Cursor Rules for Carbon DBH Project

## Language Preference
- Always respond in English
- All code comments and documentation should be in English
- All user-facing messages should be in English

## Code Style
- Use snake_case for Python variables and functions
- Use descriptive variable names
- Add docstrings to all functions
- Follow PEP 8 style guidelines

## Project Structure
- Keep data files in Data/ directory
- Keep scripts in src/ directory
- Keep models in Models/ directory
- Keep plots in plots/ directory

